    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow business to use Apprenticeship Levy pots for cash flow during Coronavirus",
        "additional_details": "This would be a quick and administratively relatively easy access for businesses, because they all have their own accounts set up already.",
        "background": "I want the government to support the cash flow of businesses during the Coronavirus outbreak by using the levy pot funds (\u00a3millions) that businesses have paid in, but not yet used. Business survival rather than training is a priority at the moment.",
